How I make a Chemex with @drinktrade
- 40g of medium course gound coffee
- 120ml bloom
- First pour up to 400ml
- Final pour up to 600ml
I use a 1:15 ratio of coffee to water with a brew time of rougly 5 minutes. Check out the link in by bio to learn more about Trade and get a free bag of coffee with your first subscription!
